ClusterSignificanceExtras
  • Reference

Hundred overlap dataset.

Output from the zeroOrHundred function with overlap argument = 100 and other default arguments.

hundred

Format

list of arrays

list names

The number of points per group.

list elements

An array containing all repititions of the ClusterSignificance input matrix for the specific points number indicated in the list element name

array dimension 1

Rows of the input matrix to ClusterSignificance.

array dimension 2

Columns of the input matrix to ClusterSignificance.

array dimension 3

The repititions for each points per group amounts.

Value

list of arrays

Examples

hundred
